translations: vi.闯入，干涉，侵占他人权益；无执照营业（interlope 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.sentence: The idea of judge made-law was first interloped clearly by Cardozo and has had a vital significance in the area of the administration of justice in the United States.
sentences.translation: 法官立法思想，由卡多佐第一次明确地提出来，在当时的美国司法领域具有举足轻重的意义。
